{"tid":807046,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【連登教學】完全封鎖會員功能","createTime":"2018-09-05T08:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T13:42:08.000Z","uid":149978,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7e13f2540c046c62acb8ab8e3161334dc912dd92","tid":807046,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:06:43.000Z","msg":"連登係一個公眾討論區<br />\n但經常會有人因政治、宗教、哲學觀、價值觀不合而吵架。<br />\n良性辯論和吵架係好事。<br />\n<br />\n但網上世界同現實世界都好，<br />\n都好容易演化成衝突，面左左，<br />\n變成惡性語言人身攻擊，<br />\n損人不利己，又浪費時間，又影衰自己在網上世界的網名。<br />\n<br />\n與其互相人身攻擊，狗咬狗骨<br />\n不如「道不同不相為謀」，直接封鎖對方<br />\n<br />\n以前，連登的封鎖，會有show blocked user，忍唔住又解封返。<br />\n<br />\n今年3月開始，連登已經推出左「完全封鎖功能」，完全封鎖，唔會再有show blocked user出現，連引用的回覆內容都會block。<br />\n<br />\n日後，大家可以開心用連登，唔駛怕煩膠。"},{"pid":"1d4d86bc8c927bb06742bdceb7323ab1ef6389f3","tid":807046,"uid":33643,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:10:12.000Z","msg":"完全封鎖「KMeansClustering」後將隱藏所有該會員的主題、回覆及被引用回覆。如日後需解除封鎖，請於「帳號」內的「封鎖會員」中設定。"},{"pid":"d7bc12765e61d684e60c67c92d77d8fc49d108d2","tid":807046,"uid":149978,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:11:17.000Z","msg":"教學<br />\n<br />\n按一下會員的資料<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/160823_1b4335a97a9d9f9d45b26a06d18c7f3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F160823_1b4335a97a9d9f9d45b26a06d18c7f3c.jpg&h=d0d48483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n按封鎖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/160855_bdc14a715796ce49e9a8eaea24d5bc65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F160855_bdc14a715796ce49e9a8eaea24d5bc65.jpg&h=d58b1d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n按完全封鎖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/160925_ceab4bbba637395b214325ebd6513cbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F160925_ceab4bbba637395b214325ebd6513cbe.jpg&h=e1390e70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n謝謝<br />\n<br />\n展望：<br />\n如果連登admin加入埋永久封鎖，同雙向完全封鎖（封鎖他後，他也不能見到我），會更佳。"},{"pid":"43c64c0bd1d47870b78c14bc74976630301bb813","tid":807046,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1d4d86bc8c927bb06742bdceb7323ab1ef6389f3","tid":807046,"uid":33643,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:10:12.000Z","msg":"完全封鎖「KMeansClustering」後將隱藏所有該會員的主題、回覆及被引用回覆。如日後需解除封鎖，請於「帳號」內的「封鎖會員」中設定。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:12:04.000Z","msg":"表示尊重"},{"pid":"e14ac8e103fd508393639c985ebd946101b9dcf8","tid":807046,"uid":179938,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:12:32.000Z","msg":"清坐咗幾耐？"},{"pid":"1e820cd48893a81291f3bcaa5e066054d3292c5a","tid":807046,"uid":51021,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/165346_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F165346_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f74f5821&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/165349_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F165349_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2fc23d89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成日開完膠post 唔夠人講 就扮受害者 真係好撚肉鳩酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8177cec7beaa1aaea299a4ad63734116526515","tid":807046,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:41:34.000Z","msg":"呢個世界真係有些人係痴線的<br />\n 又要玩人身攻擊，因人廢言<br />\n又唔封鎖<br />\n所以出此post教學<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/806629/page/1?post=3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\"